_source.text: [0056] The curable composition of the present invention, which includes a reactive silyl group-containing organic polymer (A) as the main component, is better in compatibility with a curing catalyst, namely the amidine compound (B), as compared with a composition which includes, as the main component, such an inorganic polymer as polydimethylsiloxane.
